# {{surname|zh|xlit=Zhe}}

======Usage notes======
In Chinese, discounts are expressed in number of tenths of the original price instead of percentage off.

For discounts not in tenths, {{zh-m|點|decimal point}} is omitted, e.g. {{zh-m|[[七]][[五]][[折]]|qīwǔ zhé}} means 75% of the original price, i.e. 25% off.

